## Title and Description Optimization
- **Page Title**: "DreamfinityX - AI Image Generator & Editor"
- **Meta Description**: Focus on functionality and immediate value
- **H1 Tag**: Clear, descriptive main heading
- **H2 Tags**: Descriptive section headings

## Image SEO
- **Alt Text**: Descriptive alt attributes for all images
- **File Names**: Descriptive names for uploaded images
- **Next.js Image**: Use optimized Image component
- **Responsive Images**: Proper sizing and formats

## Performance Optimizations
- **Lazy Loading**: Load SEO content after main function
- **Code Splitting**: Separate SEO components
- **Optimized Images**: WebP format where supported
- **Minimal JavaScript**: Only necessary client-side code

## Avoid SEO Anti-Patterns
❌ Keyword stuffing in content
❌ Hidden text or links
❌ Slow loading hero sections
❌ Non-functional design elements
❌ Duplicate content
❌ Poor mobile experience

